=== quiet ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
  ~ [2] copy > static page
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
  ~ [6] copy > config file
=== v ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
  ~ [2] copy > static page
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
  + [5] service > restart web
  ~ [6] copy > config file
=== vv ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
      |- dir          state  (absent) -> directory
      `- ensure_mode  perm   (absent) -> -rwxr-xr-x
  ~ [2] copy > static page
      |- ensure_mode   perm         (absent) -> -rw-r--r--
      `- ensure_owner  owner:group  (absent) -> pskry:staff
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
      `- run  check  exit 1 -> exit 0
  + [5] service > restart web
      |- ensure_service_active   +
      `- ensure_service_enabled  +
  ~ [6] copy > config file
      |- copy_file     >
      |- ensure_mode   +
      `- ensure_owner  >
